    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
}

nav a {
    color: white;
    margin: 0 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

nav a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

main {
    padding: 20px;
}

footer {
    background-color: #f1f1f1;
    color: #555;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    bottom: 0;
}
```

### **Step 4: Test Your Website**

Open each HTML file in your browser to ensure that navigation works and styles are applied correctly.

