    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

header {
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: fixed;
    width: 100%;
    top: 0;
}

nav a {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

nav a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    margin-top: 80px;
}

footer {
    background: #f4f4f4;
    color: #333;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
}

@media (min-width: 600px) {
    section {
        padding: 80px 100px;
    }
}
```

### **Step 4: Enhance Navigation Smoothness (Optional)**

To add smooth scrolling when navigation links are clicked, you can add the following CSS:

```css
html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
}
```

### **Step 5: Preview Responsiveness**

Use your browser's developer tools to test the website on various screen sizes.

