## 6. Linking CSS to HTML

To apply the CSS styles to your HTML, you need to link the `styles.css` file within the `<head>` section of your `index.html`.

```html
<head>
    <!-- Existing meta tags -->
    <title>My Simple Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
```

Now, your HTML file references the CSS file, and styles will be applied accordingly.

